Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.45,0:39:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有数据注释  其实几乎没有数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No annotating of data -- hardly any data at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.12,0:39:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来更像是消遣读物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hmm, more like summer reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.06,0:39:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们拍的片子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More like our film.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.32,0:39:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们的研究  我们真正的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whereas our work -- our real work --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.88,0:39:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远不是科夫曼医生所能及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is miles beyond Dr. Kaufman's.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.80,0:39:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的研究  会让卡夫曼医生被世人所遗忘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our work...will leave Dr. Kaufman in the dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.60,0:39:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look.
