Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的领结\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the past, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.48,0:39:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他们在拍摄过程中让你系的正规领带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that regular tie they put you in for the filming --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.75,0:39:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你也并没什么帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that wasn't doing you any favors, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.28,0:40:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.32,0:40:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不像你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.08,0:40:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在安排后续采访的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I'm, uh, scheduling these follow-up interviews now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.43,0:40:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能否给你个建议  还是继续用领结吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But may I suggest...stick with the bow tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.57,0:40:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信我会说出这种话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot...believe I am saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.74,0:40:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会仔细考虑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll take that under advisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.68,0:40:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得  我得跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need to, uh -- I need to talk to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.37,0:40:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于咱们的片子  关于这份稿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}About our film... Uh, about, uh, this manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.96,0:40:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你谈  一种可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to talk to you about a -- well, a-a possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.95,0:40:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗吉妮娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Virginia?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.53,0:40:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.93,0:40:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等赫伯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, I'm waiting for Herb.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.24,0:41:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫伯是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's Herb?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.32,0:41:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们的租户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.47,0:41:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.38,0:41:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你雇了赫伯·史普利博\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You hired Herb Spleeb?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.07,0:41:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.32,0:41:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我丈夫想要的东西给他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, to give my husband what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.16,0:41:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.03,0:41:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.97,0:41:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}George -- 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.15,0:41:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他认为我是个不称职的母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he wanted to put my fitness on trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.33,0:41:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要与我对簿公堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.85,0:41:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要让大家都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He -- he wanted to make it a matter of public record
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.97,0:41:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的工作实质上淫乱不堪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the prurient nature of our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.98,0:41:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我在这里都干了什么  和你在一起时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the hours I spend here and the hours I spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.44,0:41:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然他的律师已经开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, his lawyer had already begun asking questions
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.00,0:41:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公园广场酒店调查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at the Park Plaza Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-乔治  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- George. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.14,0:41:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-乔治要这么做  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- George is doing this. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.75,0:41:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着我们会有两次露面的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meaning we would have had two debuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.80,0:41:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边是CBS  我们将作为开创性的研究者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One on CBS, the two of us being introduced to the country
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.66,0:41:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被世人所认识  与此同时  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as groundbreaking researchers, while at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.92,0:42:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个法庭的法官将会向世界宣布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a judge in some court would also be presenting us
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.63,0:42:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一对道德沦丧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to the world as sleazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.27,0:42:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淫乱无耻的狗男女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}amoral smut peddlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.54,0:42:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能让自己陷入那种境地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You -- you -- you cannot be put in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.00,0:42:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗吉妮娅  那样你根本没有机会胜诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Virginia, that's -- that's completely untenable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.41,0:42:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So -- so what we do --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.48,0:42:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  我已经解决了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, no, no. It's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.66,0:42:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫伯这会儿正在向乔治提议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Herb is presenting an offer to George as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.40,0:42:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出的条件对乔治来说非常有利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the terms are very favorable to George.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.67,0:42:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他同意这事不上法庭就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All he has to do is keep it out of court.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.22,0:42:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.19,0:42:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.55,0:42:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't, uh --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.92,0:42:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会放弃了孩子的抚养权吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't given up your children, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.54,0:42:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.78,0:42:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦影片播出后  我就能将他们夺回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But once the film airs, I will get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.67,0:42:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗吉妮娅  你不会真...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Virginia, you didn't do --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.46,0:42:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我会用这段影片证明这份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I will use the film to show that this work --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.87,0:42:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这份工作的付出是实实在在  值得尊重的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that my part in our work is respectable and legitimate
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.87,0:42:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快有一天  我会将他拉上法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And one day, very soon, I will drag him into court
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.23,0:42:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后利用CBS的盛誉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I can use the sterling
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.41,0:42:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将孩子们夺回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}reputation of CBS to get the kids back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.42,0:42:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你不能...  你现在就得将他们夺回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you cann-- no, you have to get them back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.48,0:43:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到  这已成事实了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. I can't. It's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.68,0:43:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是暂时的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.20,0:43:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.31,0:43:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.03,0:43:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道乔治·华盛顿特别喜欢狗吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you know George Washington really loved dogs a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.15,0:43:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他最喜欢的一只叫"甜嘴"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And his favorite one was named sweet lips?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.45,0:43:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.02,0:43:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你知道希腊曾经是一座岛吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you know Greece was an island?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.36,0:43:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有个问题问你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ooh, here's my question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.28,0:43:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们爸爸和我一直在商量一件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um, your dad and I were talking about something
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.55,0:43:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们或许会感兴趣的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you might think is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.25,0:43:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去希腊吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Going to Greece?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.46,0:43:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去看波托马克河\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to go to the Potomac.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.92,0:43:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去希腊或者波托马克河\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not to greece or the Potomac.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.74,0:43:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也算是一种全新尝试吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But an adventure of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.54,0:43:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道的  现在你们平时都待在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know how -- how you spend all week here,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.59,0:43:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了周三是在爸爸那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}except for Wednesdays, when you're with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.81,0:43:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后周末的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then on the weekends,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.32,0:43:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是每隔一周就会和爸爸过周末\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's every other weekend with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.47,0:44:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有奥黛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.99,0:44:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有奥黛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.95,0:44:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的问题是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, well, my question is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.73,0:44:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都喜欢待在爸爸那边  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you like staying at your dad's place, right?
