Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.09,0:49:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们看对方的眼神  他亲吻她的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The way they looked at each other, the way he kissed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.13,0:49:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前就看过这部电影了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Y-y-you've seen this film before.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.53,0:49:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过四遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Four times.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.47,0:49:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你是想让我从中悟出些什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So...you wanted me to see something in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.92,0:49:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.42,0:49:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你看清...我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanted you to see...us --
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.59,0:49:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一对真实  混乱  复杂的情侣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a real, messy, complicated couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.06,0:49:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们拥有那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But a couple that has that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.08,0:49:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.19,0:49:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.48,0:50:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能为了我不放弃这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you not give up on this with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.87,0:50:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.99,0:50:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书的事还好办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, the book part was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.99,0:50:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给那伤透我女儿心的混球打了个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I called up that reprobate that broke my daughter's heart
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.18,0:50:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得很明白  这是他欠我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and made it very clear he owed me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.34,0:50:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但把书交给竞争对手电视台\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Getting the book to a competing network --
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.06,0:50:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得花一番功夫了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that, uh... took a little more doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.31,0:50:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的关系网依然神通广大  巴顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you're still a connected man, Barton,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.05,0:50:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不管你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because whatever you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.40,0:50:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我们的影片正式流产了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1} our film is now officially dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.70,0:50:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你看起来会更高兴呢  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you'd look happier about that, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.74,0:50:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你想要的  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was what you wanted, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.50,0:50:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打给我不就是为了这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, why you called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.23,0:51:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.35,0:51:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就直说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.02,0:51:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的研究远胜于科夫曼的  你很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your work is better than Kaufman's. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.49,0:51:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是还没准备好向世人展示罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You just aren't ready to show it to the world yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.11,0:51:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用自己赌了一把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You bet on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.93,0:51:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把弗吉妮娅也赌上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I bet on Virginia, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.09,0:51:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话给你时  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What I, uh -- what I didn't realize when I called you was...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.97,0:51:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗吉妮娅正在与前夫争夺孩子的抚养权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Virginia was in the middle of a custody dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.22,0:51:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏影片这件事  你告诉过弗吉妮娅吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You did tell Virginia you were killing the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.44,0:51:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来准备告诉她的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I-I was gonna tell her, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.59,0:51:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一直忙于制定对策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was just, uh, setting the wheels in motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.83,0:51:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保一切能按计划进行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}getting all the -- the pieces in -- in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.49,0:51:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你已经决定好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After you already decided
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.88,0:51:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要如何做之后吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what you were going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.72,0:51:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  如果能收回我的选择  我一定...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Believe me, if I co-- if I could take it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.90,0:51:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You would.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.81,0:51:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.17,0:52:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我想起你在妇产科医院时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That reminds me of when you wanted your study
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.78,0:52:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你的研究所做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at Maternity Hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.38,0:52:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有尽力说服我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And instead of trying to convince me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.56,0:52:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的  而是威胁我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you were right, you blackmailed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.07,0:52:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说不是要责备你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't -- I don't say that to scold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.02,0:52:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总这么一意孤行  不顾旁人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But blazing ahead like this -- always the one-man show,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.38,0:52:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只按自己的想法做事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}always your terms and your terms only --
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.98,0:52:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会让你周围的人十分难过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it's hell on the people around you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.31,0:52:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就我看来  你自己也不好受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and no picnic for you, either, as far as I could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.68,0:52:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这是什么感觉  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what it's like, Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.88,0:52:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活在恐惧之中  不敢让别人进入内心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Living scared -- scared to let people in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.48,0:52:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如今我过回了简单的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why my life is simple now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.34,0:52:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小诊所里做回普通医生  规律的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Being a doctor again, working at a clinic, steady routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.57,0:52:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说一切都回复如初了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not saying everything is fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.45,0:52:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛格丽特虽然没有离开我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, Margaret hasn't left me,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.57,0:53:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今她只沉浸在自己的世界中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Although... what she does with her time...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.60,0:53:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下了一个决心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I took a leap of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.09,0:53:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定相信她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Decided to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.83,0:53:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉了她一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told her. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.94,0:53:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算很艰难  但至少我们如今一起面对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As tough as it's been, at least we're in it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.83,0:53:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未想过...伤害弗吉妮娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I-I never meant... to hurt Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.13,0:53:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.43,0:53:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从不是有意的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.72,0:54:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能这么继续下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This has got to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.92,0:54:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.84,0:54:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.22,0:54:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.69,0:54:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话不完全对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not entirely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.20,0:54:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.68,0:54:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫这么多年来一直有外遇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that my husband has been having an affair for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.80,0:54:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去我总假装这不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I-I used to just pretend that it wasn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.82,0:54:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我假装视而不见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then I looked the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.04,0:54:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将心思都放在孩子们身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then I focused on my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.14,0:54:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  我遇见了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then...I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.44,0:54:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.59,0:54:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know that this... 
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.12,0:54:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}thing that we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.94,0:55:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这是我想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know that I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.51,0:55:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is something that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.12,0:55:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想感受这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know I want to feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.81,0:55:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车队刚刚到达首府\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The motorcade has just arrived at the capitol
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.17,0:55:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有权贵已经聚集于此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where the attending dignitaries
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.85,0:55:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备参加总统就职典礼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have assembled for the inaugural ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.51,0:55:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今正在就座的是肯尼迪家族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now taking their seats are members of the Kennedy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.25,0:55:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪夫人及其母亲...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs. Kennedy with her mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.92,0:55:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡路里燃烧弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cal-o-metric,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.46,0:55:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天三粒  唤醒全新自我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where the new you is just three small tablets away.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.56,0:55:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.92,0:55:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...当选副总统的林登·贝恩斯·约翰逊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vice president-elect Lyndon Baines Johnson,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.84,0:55:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后出场的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the last to take his place,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.78,0:55:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本届当选总统  约翰·菲茨杰拉德·肯尼迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}President-elect John Fitzgerald Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.05,0:55:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.06,0:55:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然不带礼帽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No top hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.10,0:56:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜鲁门总统  尊敬的牧师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}President Truman, reverend clergy,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.61,0:56:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位公民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}fellow citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.01,0:56:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们见证的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We observe today
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.76,0:56:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是政党的胜利  而是自由的胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not a victory of party but a celebration of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.57,0:56:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此我向你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For I have sworn before you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.28,0:56:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and almighty God
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.71,0:56:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许下我们祖先170多年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the same solemn oath our forebears prescribed
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.36,0:56:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样许下的神圣誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}nearly a century and three-quarters ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.69,0:56:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这象征着结束  也是开端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}symbolizing an end, as well as a beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.89,0:56:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表着更新，也是变革\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}signifying renewal, as well as change.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.45,0:56:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先辈为之奋斗的理念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For which our forebears fought
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.44,0:56:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍争议于世界每个角落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are still at issue around the globe --
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.86,0:56:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那理念就是  人的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The belief that the rights of man
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.30,0:56:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井非来自国家的慷慨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}come not from the generosity of the state,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.63,0:56:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是上帝的恩赐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but from the hand of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.17,0:56:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道你们一定很失望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know that we've failed you both --
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.12,0:56:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们向我们倾诉了经历的挣扎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you've shared your struggles with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.92,0:57:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我们能研究出治疗方案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And trusted us to devise a-a treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.43,0:57:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们却没有任何实质性进展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}yet we made little discernable progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.75,0:57:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟糕的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And -- and worst of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.38,0:57:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的尝试方式打击了你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our approach discouraged you,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.43,0:57:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们感到绝望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}filled you with despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.77,0:57:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们不认为一切就该到此为止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we don't think that has to be the end of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.68,0:57:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经研究出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have developed --
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.72,0:57:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在研究一种治疗方案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are in the process of developing a protocol --
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.47,0:57:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种回到过去的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A path back, if you will --
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.26,0:57:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照这些步骤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Steps that you can follow --
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.86,0:57:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你们就可以找回幸福的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that may lead you back to a happy life,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.53,0:57:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完整而满足的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a full and satisfying life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.81,0:57:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但重点是  这需要你们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the key is, it takes both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.69,0:57:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定决心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to make a leap of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.40,0:57:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.65,0:57:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起努力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.86,0:57:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同进退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In it...together.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.82,0:57:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.37,0:57:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  不要忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We dare not forget today
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.16,0:58:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是第一次革命的继承者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that we are the heirs of that first revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.83,0:58:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让所有的朋友与敌人都听到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let the word go forth from this time and place
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.61,0:58:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我此时此刻的这番话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to friend and foe alike...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.66,0:58:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,革命的火炬已经传给了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the torch has been passed
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.42,0:58:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一代的美国人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to a new generation of Americans --
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.72,0:58:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生于这个世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}born in this century...

